    <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
    <p>
      When you interact with FlowNova through our website forms, we may collect the following information:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Contact Form:</strong> Name, email address, inquiry type, and message content</li>
      <li><strong>Booking Form:</strong> Name, email address, company name (optional), session type, and any details you include in your message</li>
      <li><strong>Client Engagements:</strong> Information you share during discovery calls, workshops, or project engagements as needed to deliver our services</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 32px;">Information Collected Automatically</h3>
    <p>
      Our website is hosted on GitHub Pages. When you visit, standard server logs may capture basic technical data such as your IP address, browser type, and pages visited.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
      We use Microsoft Clarity and Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with our website. These tools may collect data including pages visited, time on site, clicks, scrolls, and mouse movements. Clarity may record anonymized session replays to help us improve the user experience. No passwords, payment details, or sensitive input field data are captured. This data is collected through cookies and similar technologies and is processed in aggregate form.
    </p>
  </section>

